OL,3,CScots warned of 'very high' wildfire
OL,4,Crisk amid warm weather
OL,6,FExperts are urging people to be
OL,7,Fvigilant, amid a warning that there's
OL,8,Fa 'very high risk' of wildfires in
OL,9,Fparts of Scotland.
OL,11,FThe alert was issued by the Scottish
OL,12,FFire and Rescue Service and the
OL,13,FScottish Wildfire Forum for southern
OL,14,FScotland, the central Highlands, and
OL,15,Feastern Scotland. It will remain in
OL,16,Fplace until Monday 20 July.
OL,18,FIt comes as firefighters are tackling
OL,19,Fa wildfire, which has led to the
OL,20,Fevacuation of residents in the
OL,21,FCiarngorms National Park.
