OL,3,CScots warned of 'very high' wildfire
OL,4,Crisk amid warm weather
OL,6,FThe warning was first issued on
OL,7,FWednesday 15 July following weeks of
OL,8,Fwarm weather and high temperatures.
OL,10,FThe Scottish Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Fhas urged people enjoying the outdoors
OL,12,Fto behave responsibly to reduce the
OL,13,Frisk of wildfires starting.
OL,15,FSFRS' Wildfire Tactical Advisor, Kevin
OL,16,FDingwall, said: "A very high wildfire
OL,17,Frisk is forecast across central
OL,18,Fhighlands, southern and eastern
OL,19,FScotland later this week and into the
OL,20,Fweekend.
OL,26,@xD@QOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
