OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784299698
OL,3,CScots warned of 'very high' wildfire
OL,4,Crisk amid warm weather
OL,6,F"We know many people will want to
OL,7,Fenjoy the warmer weather. If you're
OL,8,Fspending time outdoors, please do so
OL,9,Fresponsibly and take simple steps to
OL,10,Fprevent fires from starting.
OL,12,F"Hot, dry conditions increase the risk
OL,13,Fof wildfire across Scotland. Even if a
OL,14,Fwarning is not in place where you
OL,15,Flive, we ask everyone to stay vigilant.
OL,17,F"Wildfires can destroy property,
OL,18,Flandscapes and wildlife. That's why
OL,19,Fit's so important that everyone takes
OL,20,Fextra care during these conditions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
