PN,32504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784299698
OL,3,CScots warned of 'very high' wildfire
OL,4,Crisk amid warm weather
OL,6,F"Avoid lighting outdoor fires or
OL,7,Fbarbecues in affected areas, and
OL,8,Fremember that a single spark can cause
OL,9,Fsignificant damage. There is no such
OL,10,Fthing as a harmless fire.
OL,12,F"You can help by sharing wildfire
OL,13,Fwarnings with your family, friends,
OL,14,Fand any visitors."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
